Cell["\<\
We see the second term is basically the one that matters here; it\
\[CloseCurlyQuote]s the nonrelativitic kinetic energy. The first term is the \
rest mass, but it doesn\[CloseCurlyQuote]t contribute to the nonrelativistic \
dynamics.\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.99221716735923*^9, 3.992217188410947*^9}, {
  3.9922174769920673`*^9, 
  3.9922174796445704`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"ee8defab-2495-4b37-979c-\
3f0d2812cd2c"]
}, Open  ]]
}, Open  ]],

